{
  "stem": "26792.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On one of these days, when groups of young women were taken to work or somewhere, we were driven in an unknown direction, but we knew what street we were in.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we saw we were approaching-- we were approaching the house of the former Jewish banker, Schmulian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we knew there was a Perkonkrust, and we knew that would be our end, because we have never heard of anyone return from the perfecture.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some people had returned, but never from the Perkonkrust.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they usually arrested young women there, not males, very few males, only for hard work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, they drove us along Valdemara Street to number 19.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We entered a gate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We entered the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a table was placed there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Perkonkrust officers were rushing and doing things, very, very, very restless.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So a new group was brought in, and they were already eager to get the jewelry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had nothing, but there were some Jewish ladies who did have jewelry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they wrote down, they knew exactly, that the Jewish ladies would never see the jewelry again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they wrote it down proforma, as if they confiscated it temporarily, and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
